<section id="Hypervisor_Hostname_Configuration" remap="TID_7612">
	<title>Configuring Node Hostname</title>
	<procedure>
		<step>
			<para>
				To set or change the hostname select the <guilabel>Hostname</guilabel> field on the <guilabel>Network</guilabel> screen, and enter the new hostname.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select <guibutton>&lt;Apply&gt;</guibutton>, and press <keycap> Enter</keycap> to save changes to the hostname.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<para>
		The hostname has been updated.
	</para>
